CustomField.description: Processing priority of Kafka Messages with this topic relative to messages from other topics. Lower numbers have higher priority. Blank values have the lowest priority. This value is passed on and set on the related AsyncRequest record for processing.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Processing priority of Kafka Messages with this topic relative to messages from other topics. Lower numbers have higher priority. Blank values have the lowest priority. The value is passed on and set on the related AsyncRequest record for processing.
CustomField.label: Priority
